text: Bogorodskoye () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Denisovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 508 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Meleuz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Bogorodskoye, Meleuzovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
